'''反拆屋以色列人委員會'''（[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|'''Israeli Committee Against House Demolitions'''}}，簡稱{{lang|en|'''ICAHD'''}}）是一個[[非牟利|非牟利]]的倡議組織，用非暴力[[直接行動|直接行動]]，反對和抵抗以色列在其佔領區內拆毀[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]人家園。<ref>{{cite web 
 |url=http://www.icahd.org/eng/about.asp?menu=2&submenu=1 
 |title=What is ICAHD 
 |publisher=Israeli Committee Against House Demolitions 
 |accessdate=2007-08-10 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070821024037/http://www.icahd.org/eng/about.asp?menu=2&submenu=1 
 |archivedate=2007-08-21 
 }}</ref>組織創立者為1973年移居以色列的美國人權份子兼人類學教授[[杰夫·哈爾珀|杰夫·哈爾珀]]。

反拆屋以色列人委員會反對以色列持續佔領[[西岸|西岸]]和[[東耶路撒冷|東耶路撒冷]]，及建造和擴展純猶太殖民區。委員會稱「結束佔領是和平的先要條件，也是反拆屋以色列人委員會的行動的首要目標。」<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.icahd.org/eng/articles.asp?menu=6&submenu=3
 |title       = The key to Peace: Dismantling the Matrix of Control
 |author      = Jeff Halper
 |publisher   = Israeli Committee Against House Demolitions
 |accessdate  = 2007-08-10
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/68Xg3Xbds?url=http://www.icahd.org/
 |archivedate = 2012-06-19
}}</ref>委員會也關注防止「長期進行中的人權侵犯」，斷言以色列的行動正在佔領區形成一個[[種族隔離|種族隔離]]政權。<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.icahd.org/eng/campaigns.asp?menu=4&submenu=4
 |title       = A Call for an anti-apartheid campaign as Israel prepares to make its occupation permanent
 |publisher   = Israeli Committee Against House Demolitions
 |accessdate  = 2008-05-10
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20060617013226/http://www.icahd.org/eng/campaigns.asp?menu=4&submenu=4
 |archivedate = 2006-06-17
}}</ref> 

== 活動 ==
反拆屋以色列人委員會活動包括發表書籍和文章，論述以色列在[[西岸|西岸]]和[[加沙|加沙]]的佔領、國際倡導活動、及在當地的抗議及非暴力抵抗行動。委員會也通由以色列、巴勒斯坦和國際志願者網絡，組織重建被拆毀的巴勒斯坦房屋。<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://icahd.org/eng/news.asp?menu=5&submenu=1&item=401
 |title       = Announcing - 2007 ICAHD Summer Rebuilding Experience July 14 – July 29, 2007
 |publisher   = Israeli Committee Against House Demolitions
 |date        = 2006-12-11
 |accessdate  = 2007-08-10
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/68Xg4bjOp?url=http://www.icahd.org/
 |archivedate = 2012-06-19
}}</ref>除了重建房屋，反拆屋以色列人委員會亦經常代表被拆屋或受到拆屋恐嚇的巴勒斯坦人採取法律行動。

反拆屋以色列人委員會成員有很多次由於嘗試阻止拆毀巴勒斯坦人家園，被以色列軍隊和警察拘捕。最近一次在2008年4月3日，委員會統籌[[杰夫·哈爾珀|杰夫·哈爾珀]]非暴力地抗議拆毀在[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]一個巴勒斯坦社區的哈姆丹家的房屋時，第八次被捕。這房屋是以前曾被以色列當局拆毀，委員會後來重建的。<ref name="online journal">{{cite news 
 |url=http://onlinejournal.com/artman/publish/article_3149.shtml 
 |title=American Israeli Jeff Halper arrested for the 8th time in Jerusalem 
 |publisher=Online Journal 
 |date=2008-04-08 
 |accessdate=2008-05-19 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821160816/http://onlinejournal.com/artman/publish/article_3149.shtml 
 |archivedate=2008-08-21 
 }}</ref>  

通常反拆屋以色列人委員會在上午5時收到一個巴勒斯坦家庭的電話，告知推土機已經到達。委員會發出行動警示，多個不同團體的活躍份子便會出動，進行抵擋推土機的[[公民抗命|公民抗命]]。<ref name = "online journal"/>

== 資金 ==
反拆屋以色列人委員會網站稱，其“活動……依靠以色列及外國的個人和團體的捐助。反拆屋以色列人委員會也獲得[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]的資助。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.icahd.org/eng/support.asp?menu=7&submenu=1 |title='How you can help' (icahd.org) |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2008-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924024233/http://icahd.org/eng/support.asp?menu=7&submenu=1 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>例如，2005年歐盟藉由和平夥伴關係計劃，給予委員會€472 786，以資助其項目「再構想：給以色列公眾一個連貫的和平範例」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.euromedinfo.eu/site.300.content.en.html |title='Middle East Peace Projects' (euromedinfo.eu) |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2009-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131235256/http://www.euromedinfo.eu/site.300.content.en.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.delisr.ec.europa.eu/english/content/cooperation_and_funding/3.asp |title='EU Partnership for Peace Programme' by European commision's delegation to Israel |accessdate=2008-12-29 |archive-date=2008-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080314173556/http://www.delisr.ec.europa.eu/english/content/cooperation_and_funding/3.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

